de; and the people </div><div class="t m41c x27 he y109c ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">to one another. So all who are united to </div><div class="t m4c8 x27 he y14e8 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Christ will receive from Him the bread of </div><div class="t macf x27 he yfc0 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">life, the heavenly food, and impart it to oth-</div><div class="t m8d4 x27 he y13e3 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ers.&quot;—The </div><div class="t m149b x55 h21 y46e ff6 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Desire of Ages, </div><div class="t m204f x82 he y46e ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">page 369. </div><div class="t m104a x18 he ye32 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">3. </div><div class="t m983 x29 he ye32 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">To what conclusion did the peo-</div><div class="t m3e2 x27 he y139a ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ple, come when they saw this miracle </div><div class="t m114b x27 he y895 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">take place? John 6:14. </div><div class="t m334a x26 h3a y121e ff4 fs1a fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">NOTE.—&quot;The </div><div class="t m2be xd he ya97 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">readiness with which the </div><div class="t m65f x27 he yc80 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">common people of Galilee were willing to </div><div class="t m1308 x27 he ya4f ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">accept Jesus as the Messiah indicates both </div><div class="t m328 x27 he y7dd ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">how general was the expectation of a Sav-</div><div class="t m992 x27 he yed0 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">iour and how great the popularity of Jesus </div><div class="t m1b5 x27 he y1267 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">had now become. He had already shown </div><div class="t md10 x27 he y12d9 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Himself to be a leader of men; they knew </div><div class="t m31d x27 he yf4a ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">He could heal any who might be wounded </div><div class="t m213 x27 he ya19 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">in battle; now they saw that He could fur-</div><div class="t m433 x27 he y7e2 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">nish an army with food ! Surely 